data.description: Welcome to this MOVE-IN READY 3 bedrooms 2 bathroom beautiful home!! This home is being sold AS IS with major appliances included such as brand new Washer and Dryer and a HOT TUB. The Home has been converted into a very modern setting from the app controlled lighting in the bathrooms and kitchen area to the garage door openers, this is the perfect small oasis for a First Time Homebuyer. Lovely screened-in porch fenced-in backyard with a Shed included. The home was recently freshly painted on interior. NO FLOOD INSURANCE is required. Seller is very motivated. Schedule your private showing before it's gone.    ONE OF THE FEW PROPERTIES IN HOLIDAY NOT LOCATED IN A FLOOD ZONE. DO NOT MISS THIS OPPPORTUNITY.
